quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  16,22,"Nyasaye wenyu ni Nyasaye mulala, ne balia abalasuubilanga mwikulu tawe emioyo chiabu chikhayanga nabo belolanga"
  16,23,"Toto bwene Nyasaye yamanya akamufisanga nende akamuretsanga habulafu, toto ye shiyachama abelolanga tawe"
  16,24,"Ne nibarebwa mbu nishina shia Nyasaye wenyu yeshiye? Nibaboola mbu: “ni tsingano tsiakhalesa tsiobubeyi.”"
  16,25,"Kho bachinge emisiko chiabu emilamba inyanga yeyindukho, nende emisiko chiabalia ababakosinjia khukhubula obumanyi. Koo ni amabii kali karie kano kabachinganga"